# Cursor Rules for notacompany.com

## Project Overview

**notacompany.com** is an interim technical talent acquisition company providing exceptional technical talent for ambitious consumer product companies. This Next.js website serves as the marketing platform for our talent placement services.

### Business Context
- **Service**: Interim technical talent acquisition for consumer product companies
- **Focus**: 3-12 month engagements for senior technical roles
- **Unique Selling Points**: 
  - Consumer product experience focus
  - Rapid deployment (2-4 weeks from brief to start)
  - Proven track record with successful exits and acquisitions
  - Practice what we preach through our own creations
- **Target Audience**: Ambitious consumer product companies, startups, scale-ups
- **Contact**: hey@notacompany.com

### Website Purpose
- Showcase services and past client successes
- Drive inquiries through email contact
- Establish credibility and expertise in consumer products
- Present our own creations as proof of capability

